data.description: Beautifully maintained single-story, 4-bedroom house, in a very desirable area. There are so many coveted features in this home. It is west-facing and has laminate flooring throughout the common areas. The home is pet-free and smoke-free. Great for someone with environmental sensitivities. The location is ideal with easy access to both I-84 & 30/32. Walking distance to Skyway Elementary & Vision Charter School. This is better than new construction, as all the landscaping and fencing have already been completed. Reach out to schedule your appointment now!
